otherNames: Otaku Elf; A Sloven Elf Who Have Been from the Edo Period, Shut-In Elf;  江戸前エルフ
synopsis: Koito Koganei works as the teenage shrine maiden at the Takamimi Shrine, catering to the whims of its resident: a centuries-old elf who loves video games as much as she hates going outside! Line up your offerings for the otaku elf—some energy drinks, chips, and video games will do nicely—and watch her new friends scramble to keep up!
